      "type": "TextBlock",
      "text": "A Washington County judge expanded the Santolla v. Katz injunction to bar every Virginia law-enforcement agency and Commonwealth's Attorney from enforcing the AWB/mag ban, effective July 21. AG Jones's bid to keep the order narrow was rejected (\"treacherous patchwork\").",
